{"tid":1459823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想記者幫忙問一問：關於警方難於分辨，分不清是否喬裝問題","createTime":"2019-08-12T22:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T22:12:46.000Z","uid":54272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d600819043bf30fb58baa376b559802853594af7","tid":1459823,"uid":54272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:04:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果</span>我，或路過見到一位路人被一個持武器既人毆打，或者按倒地上，我怕有生命危險，而對方又無表明身分執法，或者對方無任何證明其執法身分，當情況危急之下，根據自身安全自衛而反制對方，而令佢受傷或身亡，是否合法？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/自衛殺人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB24lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=959a56fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/自衛殺人</a><br />\n<br />\n我都係問下姐，如果二哥話唔得既，咁如果日後有人一邊高呼自己係警察，一邊毆打防暴警察，咁應唔應該阻止其喬裝執法？<br />\n<br />\n同埋我身上有螢光棒，算唔算冒警？"},{"pid":"568d4ba55adb476e841f6c4cc9ee06c2ede7ca51","tid":1459823,"uid":48767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:06:20.000Z","msg":"起火都唔敢，仲講殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5a0cf4e1b6a05988c5760b3e6add323aea5b64","tid":1459823,"uid":54272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"568d4ba55adb476e841f6c4cc9ee06c2ede7ca51","tid":1459823,"uid":48767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:06:20.000Z","msg":"起火都唔敢，仲講殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:12:46.000Z","msg":"我真係好想知答案"}]}